daily_summary.headline: SpaceX Starlink Launch Highlights a Busy Day in Space

top_events.title: SpaceX Falcon 9 Launches Starlink Group 17-34
top_events.description: A batch of 24 satellites for the Starlink mega-constellation launched from Vandenberg Space Force Base, California.
top_events.action: Watch live stream for real-time coverage.

top_events.title: Aurora Viewing Opportunity
top_events.description: Potential aurora activity with Kp index reaching 4.67, visible at high latitudes.
top_events.action: Check visibility if located above 65° latitude.

top_events.title: Smart Dragon 3 Launch Delayed
top_events.description: The launch of Smart Dragon 3 carrying an unknown payload has been delayed to February 12.
top_events.action: Stay updated for rescheduled launch time.

opportunities.recommendation: Possible aurora at high latitudes. Best for northern locations (65°+). Worth checking if conditions are optimal.
